Porting:
--------
	Porting menas that there is a source code (Boot loader and Kernel) avilable and it only needs to fine-tuned for
target devices and it involves first stage bootloader, second stage bootloader and linux kernal porting.

Folders Structure :
-------------------

boot        : Bootloader source code
doc         : Documents related to the mini2440
final_image : Holds the images {u-boot.bin and uImage}
install.sh  : Script to install the required packages
kernel      : Kernel source code
root_fs     : Holds root file system
serial_bin  : serial USB downloaders which is required to flash the u-bootbin
tool_chain  : Holds the required tool chain {arm-linux-*}

